{
  "stem": "27129.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they had to go over a river, you know, and without crossing that river, you couldn't leave that place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You see, the Russians knew where to build those, those, those places for forced labor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't forced labor for them yet, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they had to go, and they had a [? pram. ?] You know, you know what a [? pram ?] is?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's like, like a, a platform to take over, uh, the stuff on the, on the other side, you know, like, like heavy machinery or stuff like that, you see.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for that, there was an operator, you know, with a motor, and it went with the line, you know, across.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they had to go to that operator.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, I mean, that operator was working with the KGB.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he called up, and he said, we got, oh, five or six people, you know, that are trying to run away, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the KGB came, and they, they put them in, in a slave labor camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had to do the same kind of work, you know, but under, under a gun, you see.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after three and a half years, it's a good thing he was a barber.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wouldn't survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was such a hard work, terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But somebody found out from the, from the, the guards, you know, that he's a barber, so he, he shaved him, and he cut his hair, and then somebody higher found out, you know.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he had already a little bit, you know-- he knew the right people, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he had it-- he became officially a barber over there in that camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And who did he cut hair?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, all these people, the big, big shots, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
